
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>IPQ-GREA</title>


	  <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/geral.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/dashboard.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/cows.css" />

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins:600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a81368914c.js"></script>
	  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    
  </head>
  <body>
 
    <%- include('parts/background') %>
    
    <%- include('parts/menu') %>

    <div class="principal">
      <h2>CLINICAL OPIATE WITHDRAWAL SCALE (COWS)</h2>

      <%- include('parts/testehead') %>

      <form class="COWS" action="/editarCOWS?idTeste=<%= COWS.id %>&idPaciente=<%= Paciente.id %>" method="POST">

        <div style="display: none;">
          <input type="submit" name="prevent-enter-submit" onclick="return false;">
        </div>

        <div>
          <p>For Buprenorphine/naloxone induction: Enter scores at time zero, 1-2 h after first dose, and at additional times that buprenorphine/naloxone is given over the induction period.</p>
        </div>
        <br>

        <div class="avgrid">

          <div class="questao">
            Resting Pulse Rate: (record beats per minute) Measured after patient is sitting/lying for one minute.
          </div>

          
          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ1" <% if (COWS.AQ1 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. pulse rate 80 or below
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="1" name="AQ1" <% if (COWS.AQ1 == '1') {%> checked <%} %> >
              1. pulse rate 81-100
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="2" name="AQ1" <% if (COWS.AQ1 == '2') {%> checked <%} %> >
              2. pulse rate 101-120
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="4" name="AQ1" <% if (COWS.AQ1 == '4') {%> checked <%} %> >
              4. pulse rate greater than 120
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <br>
        <hr>
        <br>

          <div class="avgrid5">

          <div class="questao">
            Sweating: Over past 1⁄2 hour not accounted for by room temperature or patient activity.
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ2" <% if (COWS.AQ2 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. no report of chills of flushing
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="1" name="AQ2" <% if (COWS.AQ2 == '1') {%> checked <%} %> >
              1. one subjective report of chills or flushing
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="2" name="AQ2" <% if (COWS.AQ2 == '2') {%> checked <%} %> >
              2. flushed or observable moistness on face
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="3" name="AQ2" <% if (COWS.AQ2 == '3') {%> checked <%} %> >
              3. beads of sweat on brow or face
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="4" name="AQ2" <% if (COWS.AQ2 == '4') {%> checked <%} %> >
              4. sweat streaming off face
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <br>
        <hr>
        <br>

          <div class="avgrid">

          <div class="questao">
            Restlessness: Observation during assessment.
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ3" <% if (COWS.AQ3 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. able to sit still
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="1" name="AQ3" <% if (COWS.AQ3 == '1') {%> checked <%} %> >
              1. report difficulty sitting still, but is able to do so
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="3" name="AQ3" <% if (COWS.AQ3 == '3') {%> checked <%} %> >
              3. frequent shifting or extraneous movements of legs/arms
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="5" name="AQ3" <% if (COWS.AQ3 == '5') {%> checked <%} %> >
              5. unable to sit still for more than a few seconds
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

          <br>
          <hr>
          <br>

          <div class="avgrid">

          <div class="questao">
            Pupil Size:
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ4" <% if (COWS.AQ4 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. pupils pinned or normal size for room light
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="1" name="AQ4" <% if (COWS.AQ4 == '1') {%> checked <%} %> >
              1. pupils possibly larger than normal for room light
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="2" name="AQ4" <% if (COWS.AQ4 == '2') {%> checked <%} %> >
              2. pupils moderately dilated
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="5" name="AQ4" <% if (COWS.AQ4 == '5') {%> checked <%} %> >
              5. pupils so dilated that only rim of the iris is visible
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

          <br>
          <hr>
          <br>
          
        <div class="avgrid">

          <div class="questao">
            Bone or Joint aches: If patient was having pains previously, only the additional component attributed to opiate withdrawal is scored.
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ5" <% if (COWS.AQ5 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. not present
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="1" name="AQ5" <% if (COWS.AQ5 == '1') {%> checked <%} %> >
              1. mild diffuse discomfort
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="2" name="AQ5" <% if (COWS.AQ5 == '2') {%> checked <%} %> >
              2. patient reports severe diffuse aching of joints/muscles
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="4" name="AQ5" <% if (COWS.AQ5 == '4') {%> checked <%} %> >
              4. patient is rubbing joints or muscles and is unable to sit still because of discomfort
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

          <br>
          <hr>
          <br>
          
        <div class="avgrid">

          <div class="questao">
            Runny nose or tearing: Not accounted for by cold symptoms or allergies.
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ6" <% if (COWS.AQ6 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. not present
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="1" name="AQ6" <% if (COWS.AQ6 == '1') {%> checked <%} %> >
              1. nasal stuffiness or unusually moist eyes
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="2" name="AQ6" <% if (COWS.AQ6 == '2') {%> checked <%} %> >
              2. nose running or tearing
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="4" name="AQ6" <% if (COWS.AQ6 == '4') {%> checked <%} %> >
              4. nose constantly running or tears streaming down cheeks
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <br>
        <hr>
        <br>
        
      <div class="avgrid5">

          <div class="questao">
            GI Upset: Over last 1⁄2 hour
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ7" <% if (COWS.AQ7 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. no GI symptoms
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="1" name="AQ7" <% if (COWS.AQ7 == '1') {%> checked <%} %> >
              1. stomach cramps
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="2" name="AQ7" <% if (COWS.AQ7 == '2') {%> checked <%} %> >
              2. nausea or loose stools
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="3" name="AQ7" <% if (COWS.AQ7 == '3') {%> checked <%} %> >
              3. vomiting or diarrhea 
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="5" name="AQ7" <% if (COWS.AQ7 == '5') {%> checked <%} %> >
              5. multiple episodes of diarrhea or vomiting
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

      <br>
      <hr>
      <br>
      
        <div class="avgrid">

          <div class="questao">
            Tremor: Observation of outstretched hands
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ8" <% if (COWS.AQ8 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. no tremor
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="1" name="AQ8" <% if (COWS.AQ8 == '1') {%> checked <%} %> >
              1. tremor can be felt, but not observed
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="2" name="AQ8" <% if (COWS.AQ8 == '2') {%> checked <%} %> >
              2. slight tremor observable
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="4" name="AQ8" <% if (COWS.AQ8 == '4') {%> checked <%} %> >
              4. gross tremor or muscle twitching
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <br>
        <hr>
        <br>
        
          <div class="avgrid">
  
          <div class="questao">
            Yawning: Observation during assessment
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ9" <% if (COWS.AQ9 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. no yawning
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="1" name="AQ9" <% if (COWS.AQ9 == '1') {%> checked <%} %> >
              1. yawning once or twice during assessment
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="2" name="AQ9" <% if (COWS.AQ9 == '2') {%> checked <%} %> >
              2. yawning three or more times during assessment
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="4" name="AQ9" <% if (COWS.AQ9 == '4') {%> checked <%} %> >
              4. yawning several times/minute
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <br>
        <hr>
        <br>
        
          <div class="avgrid">
  
          <div class="questao">
            Anxiety or Irritability
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ10" <% if (COWS.AQ10 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. none
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="1" name="AQ10" <% if (COWS.AQ10 == '1') {%> checked <%} %> >
              1. patient reports increasing irritability or anxiousness
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="2" name="AQ10" <% if (COWS.AQ10 == '2') {%> checked <%} %> >
              2. patient obviously irritable, anxious
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="4" name="AQ10" <% if (COWS.AQ10 == '4') {%> checked <%} %> >
              4. patient so irritable or anxious that participation in the assessment is difficult
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <br>

          <div class="avgrid3">

          <div class="questao">
            Gooseflesh skin
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="0" name="AQ11" <% if (COWS.AQ11 == '0') {%> checked <%} %> >
              0. skin is smooth
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="3" name="AQ11" <% if (COWS.AQ11 == '3') {%> checked <%} %> >
              3. piloerection of skin can be felt or hairs standing up on arms
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="resposta">
            <label>
              <input type="radio" value="5" name="AQ11" <% if (COWS.AQ11 == '5') {%> checked <%} %> >
              5. prominent piloerection
            </label>
          </div>

        </div>
        <br>

          <div class="TotalScore">Total Score = <%= COWS.AQ1+COWS.AQ2+COWS.AQ3+COWS.AQ4+COWS.AQ5+COWS.AQ6+COWS.AQ7+COWS.AQ8+COWS.AQ9+COWS.AQ10+COWS.AQ11 %></div>
          <div class="BloodPressure">Blood Pressure / Pulse = <input class="nothing" name="BloodPressure" value="<%= COWS.BloodPressure %>" ></div>
          <div class="BloodPressure">Dose of Buprenorphine/naloxone Given = <input class="nothing" name="DoseGiven" value="<%= COWS.DoseGiven %>" ></div>

          Note: Give first dose when COWS score > 7<br><br>
          SCORE:<br>
          5-12 = Mild<br>
          13-24 = Moderate<br>
          25-36 = moderately severe <br>
          More than 36 = severe withdrawal<br><br>

          <div class="caixa">Última alteração: <%= COWS.updatedAt.toLocaleString('pt-BR') %> - por: <%= COWS.NomeProfissionalAvaliacao %></div><br>

        <button class="btn">SALVAR ALTERAÇÕES</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>


  </body>

</html>
